data.description: Nestled in the heart of Hutto, this single-family home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and over 1,300 square feet of living space. The spacious floor plan features a modern kitchen with updated white appliances, and plenty of cabinet space. The primary bedroom suite includes a walk-in closet, dual vanities, and a garden tub perfect for soaking after a long day. You'll love the abundance of natural light that flows throughout the home, highlighting the beautiful finishes and details. Enjoy outdoor living on the covered patio overlooking the large backyard. This home is situated in a fantastic location, with easy access to nearby shopping, dining, and entertainment. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this amazing property your own! Full Interior painting, updated kitchen appliances to include:range, microwave and dishwasher.
